e voting in santa clara county 2004 cs74n project e voting in santa clara county 2004 cs74n project ever wonder how a real election works students in the stanford freshman seminar cs74n digital dilemmas fall 2004 documented pre election testing and polling place operations in santa clara county which used the sequoia avc edge touch screen voting machines here is a description with photos of our visit to the santa clara county elections office warehouse before election day where we saw the pre election logic and accuracy tests of some of the machines here is a description also with photos of setup of the machines and polling place operations on election day
